 1 In a prior version of this table, the code SRT: T-D1217 was specified for the concept 'Maxilla and mandible'. The use of this code conflicts with its assignment to another concept in SNOMED, and its use in this context is deprecated. Although there is minimal possibility of misinterpretation with SOP Instances that may include the deprecated use, receiving applications should be aware of this change; seechapter_J
 2 In a prior version of this table, the code SRT: T-D8300 was used for(16953009, SCT, 'Elbow joint') (14975008, SCT, 'Forearm') (24136001, SCT, 'Hip') (87953007, SCT, 'Ureter') (13881006, SCT, 'Zygoma') chapter_J
 3 In a prior version of this Context Group, concepts were used that were not specific to the cross-sectional anatomy (including the full thickness of the body). Further, whether or not(113345001, SCT, 'Abdomen')

